---
export const prerender = true;
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import HeroBackground from "../components/HeroBackground.astro";
import { ClipboardList, Bot, Gem, ArrowRight, MapPin } from "lucide-react";
---

<MainLayout title="About Empower VA | Business Efficiency Specialist">
  <main class="relative min-h-screen">
    <HeroBackground />

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 z-10">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-teal-50 border border-teal-100 text-xs font-bold text-teal-800 uppercase tracking-wide mb-6"
        >
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-600"></span>
          Business Efficiency Specialist
        </div>
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight"
        >
          More Than a <br />
          <span
            class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1A565E] to-[#9F89B6] dark:from-teal-300 dark:to-purple-300"
            >Virtual Assistant</span
          >
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        >
          My journey from mastering business administration to building
          efficiency systems—and why that makes me the strategic partner you
          need.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FOUNDATION SECTION -->
    <section
      class="py-20 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-y border-slate-200"
    >
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div
          class="bg-teal-50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl border border-teal-100 shadow-sm"
        >
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
            Our Foundation: Mastering the Mechanics of Business
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-teal-700 font-semibold mb-6">
            It all started in the administrative trenches.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              My career began in traditional customer service and admin roles.
              But as a single mother to three children, the standard 9-to-5
              model was unsustainable. The need for flexibility led me to remote
              administrative work, a move that would unexpectedly redefine my
              entire career path.
            </p>
            <p>
              As a Virtual Assistant, I dove headfirst into the day-to-day
              operations of UK businesses. I wasn't just managing inboxes and
              calendars; I was on the front line, seeing exactly where systems
              broke down and where inefficiency festered. I saw a pattern: so
              much time was lost to repetitive, manual tasks. I couldn't shake
              the question, "There has to be a better way to do this."
            </p>
            <p class="font-bold text-teal-800">
              That question sparked a mission to find a better way, not just for
              me, but for my clients.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EFFICIENCY SECTION -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
            The Search for Greater Efficiency
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 font-semibold mb-6">
            From simply doing the work to optimising it.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              My mission led me to the world of automation. I discovered tools
              like Google Apps Script and realised I could build bridges between
              the disconnected systems that caused so much frustration. I
              started by automating my own admin, and the efficiency I unlocked
              was a game-changer.
            </p>
            <p>
              I immediately began applying these new skills to my clients'
              businesses. My role evolved. I was no longer just a service
              provider completing a to-do list; I became a <strong
                class="text-teal-700">business efficiency specialist</strong
              >, actively seeking out bottlenecks and building simple
              automations to eliminate them, making my core VA services more
              valuable and impactful than ever.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BIO SECTION -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-200">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="md:col-span-1">
            <div class="relative">
              <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-teal-600 to-purple-600 rounded-full rotate-6 opacity-20 blur-lg"
              >
              </div>
              <img
                src="/nicola-berry.webp"
                alt="Nicola Berry"
                class="relative w-64 h-64 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover shadow-xl border-4 border-white"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-2 text-center md:text-left">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
              A VA With a Developer's Toolkit
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              My unique journey means I bring a strategic mindset to
              administrative support. I don't just see a task; I see the entire
              process. This allows me to not only manage your daily operations
              flawlessly but also to identify opportunities for improvement that
              others might miss.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-teal-800">
              When you work with me, you get more than an extra pair of
              hands—you get a partner dedicated to making your business run
              smarter.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SCOTTISH ROOTS SECTION -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-y border-slate-200">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
        >
          <MapPin class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-600" />
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          Scottish Roots, Global Reach
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Based in the heart of Falkirk, Empower Virtual Assistant Services
          brings Scottish reliability and warmth to remote support. We pride
          ourselves on building genuine partnerships with our clients, no matter
          where they are based. Efficient, discreet, and proactive support is
          our promise.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SPECIALIST SERVICES -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
            My Specialist Services
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
            While my core focus is providing exceptional administrative support,
            my unique skillset allows me to offer specialised solutions through
            my sister brands.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- VA Services -->
          <div
            class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-teal-500 shadow-lg scale-105 relative z-10 text-center"
          >
            <div
              class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
            >
              <ClipboardList class="w-7 h-7 text-teal-600" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
              Administrative Support
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
              The foundational support that is my specialty. Reliable, proactive
              services to keep your operations running seamlessly.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/services"
              class="text-teal-700 font-bold hover:text-teal-900 inline-flex items-center gap-1"
            >
              Explore VA Services <ArrowRight class="w-4 h-4" />
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Automation -->
          <a
            href="https://empowerautomation.co.uk/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 text-center hover:border-orange-300 transition-all group"
          >
            <div
              class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            >
              <Bot class="w-7 h-7 text-orange-500" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
              Automation & Technical
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
              For businesses needing dedicated workflow automation, visit my
              specialist site, Empower Automation.
            </p>
            <span
              class="text-orange-600 font-bold group-hover:text-orange-700 inline-flex items-center gap-1"
            >
              Visit Empower Automation <ArrowRight class="w-4 h-4" />
            </span>
          </a>

          <!-- Digital Solutions -->
          <a
            href="https://empowerdigitalsolutions.co.uk/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 text-center hover:border-pink-300 transition-all group"
          >
            <div
              class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            >
              <Gem class="w-7 h-7 text-pink-500" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
              Digital Solutions
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
              For custom web apps and development, explore my dedicated brand,
              Empower Digital Solutions.
            </p>
            <span
              class="text-pink-600 font-bold group-hover:text-pink-700 inline-flex items-center gap-1"
            >
              Visit Digital Solutions <ArrowRight class="w-4 h-4" />
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA SECTION -->
    <section
      class="py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white text-center relative overflow-hidden"
    >
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/grid.svg')] opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
          Ready for Proactive Administrative Support?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Let's discuss how my unique approach to virtual assistance can bring
          new levels of efficiency and peace of mind to your business.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 transition-all shadow-xl text-lg"
        >
          Get in Touch <ArrowRight class="w-5 h-5" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
